@node Future

  @{b}- Future -@{ub}

Things to do with FileChecker in the future:

 * Include support for more file types.

 * Create a better system for recognizing pure text files, the method
   used in the current version of FileChecker is rather primitive.

 * Add more features to the "Preview File" Gui.

@endnode


  @{b}- Update listview -@{ub}
This will update the directory listview in FileCheckers Gui. Select this 
option if you have copied/deleted files or in any other way changed the
contents of the selected source dir. 


